1
00:00:51,400 --> 00:00:51,920
Boss Xingyu.

2
00:00:52,960 --> 00:00:53,840
Have you gotten hold of A Di?

3
00:00:53,880 --> 00:00:54,600
I've been calling nonstop.

4
00:00:54,600 --> 00:00:56,160
No one's picking up.

5
00:00:56,640 --> 00:00:57,280
Boss Xingyu.

6
00:00:57,840 --> 00:00:59,640
Don't your SIM cards have tracking?

7
00:01:00,080 --> 00:01:00,480
Yeah.

8
00:01:03,440 --> 00:01:04,240
Oh shit.

9
00:01:04,800 --> 00:01:06,480
Someone pulled my SIM card.

10
00:01:07,360 --> 00:01:08,760
They pulled the SIM card?

11
00:01:10,200 --> 00:01:12,360
Are they trying to steal something confidential?

12
00:01:12,800 --> 00:01:14,360
My phone's encrypted.

13
00:01:14,760 --> 00:01:16,400
No one but me can unlock it.

14
00:01:16,600 --> 00:01:18,280
Force it open and it'll self-destruct.

15
00:01:18,920 --> 00:01:20,320
If that's the case,

16
00:01:20,360 --> 00:01:22,120
then pulling the SIM won't help them.

17
00:01:23,160 --> 00:01:23,720
Tracking.

18
00:01:24,920 --> 00:01:26,560
A Di and I have our phones linked for tracking.

19
00:01:26,720 --> 00:01:27,400
He definitely doesn't know.

20
00:01:27,400 --> 00:01:29,200
Sis Fei's people took out my SIM card.

21
00:01:29,360 --> 00:01:30,920
He thought I was in danger and went to find me.

22
00:01:31,400 --> 00:01:32,080
Damn it.

23
00:01:32,880 --> 00:01:33,720
This is bad.

24
00:01:34,720 --> 00:01:36,680
Then we have no idea where he went.

25
00:01:36,680 --> 00:01:37,640
And we can't reach him.

26
00:01:37,800 --> 00:01:38,840
What do we do now?

27
00:01:41,200 --> 00:01:41,840
Su Tai.

28
00:01:42,680 --> 00:01:43,400
His boss.

29
00:01:49,160 --> 00:01:49,960
Hello?

30
00:01:50,840 --> 00:01:51,960
An encrypted satellite phone.

31
00:01:51,960 --> 00:01:54,160
It's A Di's and my emergency line.

32
00:01:54,640 --> 00:01:55,000
Okay.

33
00:01:55,320 --> 00:01:57,440
It'll be open for you in five minutes.

34
00:01:57,880 --> 00:01:59,600
Where was his last location?

35
00:02:00,200 --> 00:02:01,040
Hold on, let me check.

36
00:02:03,880 --> 00:02:05,040
It's the Death Jungle.

37
00:02:05,240 --> 00:02:06,960
No one makes it out of there alive.

38
00:02:25,840 --> 00:02:26,280
Boss.

39
00:02:26,480 --> 00:02:26,920
A Di!

40
00:02:27,200 --> 00:02:28,480
They stole my SIM to trick you.

41
00:02:28,680 --> 00:02:29,880
Don't go into the Death Jungle, no matter what.

42
00:02:29,880 --> 00:02:30,400
Too late.

43
00:02:31,480 --> 00:02:32,720
I'm already inside.

44
00:02:34,640 --> 00:02:36,240
And there's a little snake here, too.

45
00:02:36,880 --> 00:02:38,400
Doesn't look very friendly.

46
00:02:41,680 --> 00:02:42,400
Look up the venomous snake.

47
00:02:48,720 --> 00:02:50,320
This kind of snake in the Death Jungle

48
00:02:50,320 --> 00:02:51,080
has mutated.

49
00:02:51,080 --> 00:02:53,400
0.01 milligrams can kill an elephant.

50
00:02:53,680 --> 00:02:54,680
Look for its weakness.

51
00:03:00,640 --> 00:03:01,760
Hey, A Di, listen to me.

52
00:03:01,800 --> 00:03:03,200
This snake is extremely dangerous.

53
00:03:03,400 --> 00:03:04,960
They're highly territorial.

54
00:03:05,600 --> 00:03:06,320
But

55
00:03:06,640 --> 00:03:08,000
its weakness is obvious, too.

56
00:03:08,320 --> 00:03:09,600
If it locks onto you,

57
00:03:09,680 --> 00:03:10,760
wait for it to leave on its own.

58
00:03:11,320 --> 00:03:12,200
You absolutely,

59
00:03:12,280 --> 00:03:13,280
absolutely must not move.

60
00:03:20,160 --> 00:03:20,840
If I move,

61
00:03:21,280 --> 00:03:21,800
what happens?

62
00:03:22,280 --> 00:03:23,240
It'll strike instantly.

63
00:03:23,520 --> 00:03:24,680
It's seven times faster than a human.

64
00:03:25,080 --> 00:03:25,800
Once it targets you,

65
00:03:26,240 --> 00:03:27,120
you're dead for sure.

66
00:03:30,560 --> 00:03:31,280
Hey, A Di!

67
00:03:31,720 --> 00:03:32,440
A Di!

68
00:03:34,560 --> 00:03:35,720
A Di, are you okay?

69
00:03:48,400 --> 00:03:49,120
Sis.

70
00:03:49,760 --> 00:03:51,400
Don't you like that kid a lot?

71
00:03:51,880 --> 00:03:53,560
If he really dies in there,

72
00:03:54,680 --> 00:03:55,600
wouldn't that be a waste?

73
00:03:55,760 --> 00:03:58,040
I only like strong men.

74
00:03:58,640 --> 00:04:00,200
If he dies in there,

75
00:04:00,440 --> 00:04:02,400
then he wasn't my kind of man.

76
00:04:03,280 --> 00:04:04,920
How's the task I gave you coming along?

77
00:04:05,400 --> 00:04:06,920
Dawa already knows.

78
00:04:07,200 --> 00:04:07,720
He knows A Di

79
00:04:07,720 --> 00:04:09,240
went into the Death Jungle.

80
00:04:11,160 --> 00:04:13,160
Whether it's real or not,

81
00:04:13,480 --> 00:04:14,440
this bait,

82
00:04:14,920 --> 00:04:16,640
Dawa will definitely swallow it.

83
00:04:31,960 --> 00:04:32,920
Hey, A Di.

84
00:04:32,920 --> 00:04:33,760
How are you?

85
00:04:33,960 --> 00:04:34,720
Where's the snake?

86
00:04:34,720 --> 00:04:35,560
Turned it into jerky.

87
00:04:39,600 --> 00:04:41,400
You actually killed Yama's Despair.

88
00:04:41,880 --> 00:04:42,760
What's Yama's Despair?

89
00:04:43,160 --> 00:04:44,520
The savage tribes in the jungle

90
00:04:44,520 --> 00:04:45,920
call that kind of snake Yama's Despair.

91
00:04:46,520 --> 00:04:47,360
You ran into savages?

92
00:04:47,800 --> 00:04:48,880
I ran into a beauty.

93
00:04:49,480 --> 00:04:50,680
Inside the Death Jungle,

94
00:04:50,680 --> 00:04:51,560
there's a savage tribe.

95
00:04:51,680 --> 00:04:52,800
They're born hunters,

96
00:04:52,800 --> 00:04:54,000
more dangerous than snakes.

97
00:04:54,200 --> 00:04:55,320
Especially the pretty ones.

98
00:04:55,840 --> 00:04:57,240
The ones in the dark aren't scary.

99
00:04:57,560 --> 00:04:59,040
A viper in the daylight,

100
00:04:59,200 --> 00:05:00,120
even with its fangs bared,

101
00:05:00,120 --> 00:05:01,560
still can't beat a lion.

102
00:05:01,920 --> 00:05:03,840
Their weapons are coated with a toxin.

103
00:05:04,040 --> 00:05:05,440
Touch it once and you'll pass out.

104
00:05:05,920 --> 00:05:06,720
Got it.

105
00:05:06,800 --> 00:05:07,760
Got what?

106
00:05:08,120 --> 00:05:10,000
As long as she doesn't hurt me, I'm good.

107
00:05:24,200 --> 00:05:25,120
Handled it, Xingyu.

108
00:05:26,280 --> 00:05:27,320
But right now,

109
00:05:27,320 --> 00:05:28,320
I've lost my bearings.

110
00:05:28,400 --> 00:05:29,800
You need to find me a way out, fast.

111
00:05:33,360 --> 00:05:34,000
I can't.

112
00:05:34,000 --> 00:05:35,360
We've been trying from the start.

113
00:05:35,520 --> 00:05:37,040
Just keeping you on the line is our limit.

114
00:05:37,280 --> 00:05:39,120
There's heavy signal interference where you are.

115
00:05:39,120 --> 00:05:40,520
We can't track your position at all.

116
00:05:41,040 --> 00:05:41,720
Fine.

117
00:05:42,160 --> 00:05:43,160
Looks like I'm on my own.

118
00:05:43,600 --> 00:05:44,080
Oh, right.

119
00:05:44,320 --> 00:05:45,120
You be careful, too.

120
00:05:45,120 --> 00:05:45,880
You mean...

121
00:05:47,400 --> 00:05:48,080
Dawa.

122
00:06:04,400 --> 00:06:06,160
They really did break in.

123
00:06:07,920 --> 00:06:08,880
Dawa's already here.

124
00:06:08,880 --> 00:06:09,640
I gotta hang up.

125
00:06:09,640 --> 00:06:10,280
Be careful!

126
00:06:10,360 --> 00:06:11,040
Boss Xingyu.

127
00:06:11,040 --> 00:06:11,960
Find a place to hide.

128
00:06:12,040 --> 00:06:12,960
I'll round up security.

129
00:06:12,960 --> 00:06:14,400
We're not pushovers.

130
00:06:23,280 --> 00:06:24,080
Shen Xingyu.

131
00:06:24,880 --> 00:06:26,080
I know you can hear me.

132
00:06:26,800 --> 00:06:28,400
A Di isn't coming back.

133
00:06:31,200 --> 00:06:32,560
Once I find you,

134
00:06:32,960 --> 00:06:33,960
I'll have a good,

135
00:06:34,160 --> 00:06:35,560
honest talk with you.

136
00:07:35,160 --> 00:07:36,320
These useless idiots

137
00:07:37,080 --> 00:07:38,800
can't even catch a single woman.

138
00:07:40,320 --> 00:07:41,160
They couldn't have gone far.

139
00:07:41,320 --> 00:07:41,960
Go after them!

140
00:07:53,800 --> 00:07:54,800
Boss Xingyu, run!

141
00:07:57,480 --> 00:07:58,200
Shen Xingyu.

142
00:07:59,200 --> 00:08:00,440
Nowhere to run now, huh?

143
00:08:02,000 --> 00:08:03,440
Why didn't you answer earlier?

144
00:08:20,440 --> 00:08:21,240
Shen Xingyu!

145
00:08:21,600 --> 00:08:22,400
Are you insane?

146
00:08:22,400 --> 00:08:23,360
You dare fire a gun in Dongba?

147
00:08:23,600 --> 00:08:25,080
Bullshit.

148
00:08:25,080 --> 00:08:26,400
This is my damn company!

149
00:08:26,400 --> 00:08:27,600
I'll kill you!

150
00:08:27,720 --> 00:08:28,720
Holy shit...

151
00:08:29,240 --> 00:08:29,880
Boss Xingyu!

152
00:08:29,880 --> 00:08:31,240
Where'd you dig this crazy bitch up?

153
00:08:31,240 --> 00:08:32,480
She's way too hardcore.

154
00:08:32,480 --> 00:08:33,080
Shut up.

155
00:08:33,360 --> 00:08:34,160
This is my cousin.

156
00:08:34,840 --> 00:08:35,760
Shen Xingyu.

157
00:08:36,040 --> 00:08:37,400
You're a guest in Dongba.

158
00:08:37,520 --> 00:08:38,920
As long as you leave Dongba,

159
00:08:38,920 --> 00:08:40,240
we'll call it even.

160
00:08:40,240 --> 00:08:40,840
All right?

161
00:08:42,160 --> 00:08:43,280
Get the troops over here!

162
00:08:43,280 --> 00:08:44,840
I'm gonna level this place.

163
00:08:44,840 --> 00:08:45,560
What if Hong Ye...

164
00:08:45,560 --> 00:08:46,520
What if my ass!

165
00:08:46,760 --> 00:08:48,640
Just say they teamed up with Sis Fei.

166
00:08:48,920 --> 00:08:50,080
Won't Hong Ye suspect something?
